Subject: [PATCH 10/14] bgpd: rename bgp_update_.._reachability_check() to
 bgp_update_check_valid_flags()

The original function name() does not match the code implemented inside.
- As illustration, the accept_own flag is set if needed.
- This function will take into account multiple criteria to know if a
path is valid or not.

For those reasons, rename the function to
bgp_update_check_valid_flags().

Signed-off-by: Philippe Guibert <philippe.guibert@6wind.com>
---
